{"tid":1507290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香城online攻略]九月一 - 攤瘓機場","createTime":"2019-08-26T05:46:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T23:27:54.000Z","uid":58104,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"27b5bcea2970176d8bb53b69476b4b1fe70972ae","tid":1507290,"uid":58104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:46:34.000Z","msg":"大家要汲取812、813教訓：<br />\n<br />\n要點一、<br />\n防散水<br />\n<br />\n唔好太在意有冇交通可以撤退，留意抵港航班資料，接機大堂會有告示牌，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一日仲有抵港航班，就一定會有交通可以走。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n若果有抵港航班，但無車走，我地攬埋班旅客一齊攬炒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好逼我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要點二、<br />\n勿分化、割蓆<br />\n<br />\n連日累積既怒氣值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我相信有唔少人會有激動行動，如果唔認同既/怕連累你既請自行保持距離，只要唔係去到殺人呢條底線，我見唔到有咩必要去阻止。<br />\n<br />\n特別係確定捉到公安、餓底，唔該往死底打，唔認同既請離開，阻止既一律當同黨處理。<br />\n<br />\n要點三、<br />\n盡量留係機場室內範圍<br />\n<br />\n室內先係春袋、室外最多算係大脾內側，室外做戰場隨時仲難打過平時係市區。<br />\n我知GM出左通告話唔比我地入去室內，但人數夠多洗驚GM？大不了del game大家一齊棄game攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#諗到再講<br />\n#有人想知再講"},{"pid":"5b7e96727f33d2f9faebe480db523ab7f4b85206","tid":1507290,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:47:13.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY34WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=4f62aa71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"f83e3cd5f833d0e561b9c7541a6